---
import commandScreen from '../../../desktop/tests/e2e/__screenshots__/visual/05-command-palette.png';
import feedbackScreen from '../../../desktop/tests/e2e/__screenshots__/visual/08-feedback-composer.png';
import ProductFrame from './ProductFrame.astro';
---

<section class="discovery section-shell" id="discovery" aria-labelledby="discovery-title">
  <div class="section-heading" data-reveal>
    <p class="eyebrow">Progressive discovery</p>
    <h2 id="discovery-title">Power should arrive<br />when you need it.</h2>
    <p>
      The stage stays stable. The next action stays visible. Deeper controls, shortcuts, and
      commands remain one gesture away.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="showcase-grid">
    <article class="showcase-card command-card" data-reveal>
      <div class="card-copy">
        <span class="card-index">01</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Find anything. Learn nothing first.</h3>
          <p>
            Search plain language or familiar photography terms. Commands show their shortcut as
            you discover them.
          </p>
        </div>
        <span class="shortcut" aria-label="Control or Command K">
          <kbd>⌘</kbd><kbd>K</kbd>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="command-visual">
        <ProductFrame
          image={commandScreen}
          alt="Oriel command palette listing navigation, original preview, versions, copy and paste edits, and folder import"
          loading="lazy"
          label="Find a tool or action"
        />
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="showcase-card layers-card" data-reveal>
      <div class="card-copy compact">
        <span class="card-index">02</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Essentials first. Depth on request.</h3>
          <p>
            Orientation is permanent. Context appears when it matters. Expert recall stays on
            demand.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="discovery-stack" aria-label="Three levels of progressive interface depth">
        <div class="depth-layer orientation">
          <span class="depth-label">Always visible</span>
          <strong>Library&nbsp; → &nbsp;Select&nbsp; → &nbsp;Edit&nbsp; → &nbsp;Deliver</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="depth-layer context">
          <span class="depth-label">In context</span>
          <strong>Pick · Reject · Rate</strong>
          <span class="key-row"><kbd>P</kbd><kbd>X</kbd><kbd>1–5</kbd></span>
        </div>
        <div class="depth-layer depth">
          <span class="depth-label">On request</span>
          <strong>Versions · Full light controls · Crop</strong>
          <span class="plus">+</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="showcase-card feedback-card" id="feedback" data-reveal>
      <div class="feedback-visual">
        <ProductFrame
          image={feedbackScreen}
          alt="Oriel feedback mode with the Exposure control selected and a focused feedback composer"
          loading="lazy"
          label="Interface feedback mode"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="card-copy feedback-copy">
        <span class="card-index">03</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Point at what should be better.</h3>
          <p>
            Press Cmd/Ctrl + Shift + F, select any interface element, and describe the change.
            Oriel opens a reviewable GitHub issue draft—without asking for a token.
          </p>
        </div>
        <span class="shortcut wide" aria-label="Control or Command Shift F">
          <kbd>⌘/Ctrl</kbd><kbd>⇧</kbd><kbd>F</kbd>
        </span>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .discovery {
    padding-bottom: 170px;
    padding-top: 170px;
  }

  .section-heading {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .section-heading > p:last-child {
    color: var(--oriel-text-secondary);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.62;
    max-width: 610px;
  }

  .showcase-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 16px;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    margin-top: 72px;
  }

  .showcase-card {
    background:
      linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035), transparent 38%), var(--oriel-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--oriel-divider-soft);
    border-radius: 18px;
    min-height: 480px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .command-card,
  .feedback-card {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  .card-copy {
    align-items: start;
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
    grid-template-columns: 36px minmax(0, 560px) 1fr;
    padding: 34px 38px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .card-copy.compact {
    grid-template-columns: 36px 1fr;
  }

  .card-index {
    color: var(--oriel-coral);
    font-family: 'Geist Mono Variable', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    padding-top: 5px;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.4vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 540;
    letter-spacing: -0.045em;
    margin: 0 0 11px;
  }

  .card-copy p {
    color: var(--oriel-text-muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .shortcut {
    align-items: center;
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 4px;
    justify-self: end;
  }

  .shortcut kbd,
  .key-row kbd {
    align-items: center;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.17);
    border-radius: 5px;
    color: var(--oriel-text-secondary);
    display: inline-flex;
    font-family: 'Geist Mono Variable', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    height: 27px;
    justify-content: center;
    min-width: 27px;
    padding: 0 7px;
  }

  .command-visual {
    margin: 8px auto -21%;
    max-width: 1100px;
    padding: 0 34px;
    transform: perspective(1400px) rotateX(3.5deg);
    transform-origin: top center;
  }

  .layers-card {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    min-height: 560px;
  }

  .discovery-stack {
    height: 340px;
    margin: 20px auto 0;
    max-width: 720px;
    perspective: 1200px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .depth-layer {
    align-items: center;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--oriel-surface-raised) 94%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 11px;
    box-shadow: 0 28px 58px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    left: 50%;
    min-height: 94px;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    position: absolute;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: min(620px, 86%);
  }

  .depth-layer strong {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 560;
  }

  .depth-label {
    color: var(--oriel-text-muted);
    font-family: 'Geist Mono Variable', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .orientation {
    top: 0;
    z-index: 3;
  }

  .context {
    top: 92px;
    transform: translateX(-50%) scale(0.94);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .depth {
    opacity: 0.72;
    top: 176px;
    transform: translateX(-50%) scale(0.88);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .key-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .plus {
    align-items: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--oriel-divider);
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: var(--oriel-text-muted);
    display: flex;
    height: 26px;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 26px;
  }

  .feedback-card {
    align-items: center;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.14fr 0.86fr;
    min-height: 580px;
  }

  .feedback-visual {
    margin-left: -19%;
    width: 128%;
  }

  .feedback-copy {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 36px 1fr;
    padding: 52px 48px;
  }

  .feedback-copy .shortcut {
    grid-column: 2;
    justify-self: start;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  @media (hover: hover) and (pointer: fine) {
    .showcase-card {
      transition:
        border-color 220ms ease,
        transform 280ms var(--oriel-ease-out);
    }

    .showcase-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .depth-layer {
      transition:
        opacity 320ms var(--oriel-ease-out),
        transform 450ms var(--oriel-ease-out);
    }

    .layers-card:hover .context {
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(11px) scale(0.94);
    }

    .layers-card:hover .depth {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(24px) scale(0.88);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .feedback-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding-top: 30px;
    }

    .feedback-visual {
      margin-left: -9%;
      width: 118%;
    }

    .feedback-copy {
      padding-top: 24px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .discovery {
      padding-bottom: 100px;
      padding-top: 100px;
    }

    .showcase-grid {
      margin-top: 48px;
    }

    .showcase-card {
      border-radius: 12px;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .card-copy,
    .feedback-copy {
      gap: 13px;
      grid-template-columns: 28px 1fr;
      padding: 25px 20px;
    }

    .card-copy > .shortcut {
      grid-column: 2;
      justify-self: start;
    }

    .command-visual {
      margin-bottom: -12%;
      padding: 0 12px;
      transform: none;
    }

    .layers-card {
      min-height: 480px;
    }

    .discovery-stack {
      height: 285px;
    }

    .depth-layer {
      align-items: flex-start;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 17px;
    }

    .depth-layer strong {
      font-size: 10px;
    }

    .feedback-card {
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .showcase-card,
    .depth-layer {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
</style>
